# Slider

## Anatomy

- track
- range fill
- thumb
- value label
- marks

## States

- resting
- hover
- focus-visible
- dragging
- disabled
- invalid

## Variants

- single value
- range
- stepped
- with marks

## Tokens

- `--color-primary-*`
- `--color-muted`
- `--color-ring`
- `--space-*`
- `--radius-pill`

## Accessibility

- Keyboard supports Arrow keys, Home, End.
- Visible label communicates value and unit.
- Custom implementation exposes slider role and value attributes.
